webpackJsonp([81182794019823],{408:function(e,t){e.exports={data:{postBySlug:{html:'<h2 id="build-the-binary"><a href="#build-the-binary" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>Build the binary</h2>\n<p>Pull <a href="https://github.com/seanmclane/goatnickels">the repo</a> from Github to the appropriate folder in your \'src\' directory under your GOPATH then run the following.</p>\n<div class="gatsby-highlight">\n      <pre class="language-text"><code class="language-text">go install GOPATH/src/github.com/seanmclane/goatnickels</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id="or-download-the-binary"><a href="#or-download-the-binary" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>Or download the binary</h2>\n<p>Download available <a href="http://goatnickels.com/download">here</a>.</p>\n<h2 id="starting-the-server"><a href="#starting-the-server" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>Starting the server</h2>\n<p>GoatNickels ships with a default configuration file including a directory for storing the blockchain data, bootstrap nodes running a GoatNickels server, and an account value (empty). The config lives in your home directory at <code class="language-text">~/.goatnickels/config.json</code>. To write the initial config file, please run <code class="language-text">goatnickels -init-config y</code>.</p>\n<p>Then, joining the network and downloading the blockchain is as easy as running <code class="language-text">goatnickels -serve y</code>.</p>\n<div class="gatsby-highlight">\n      <pre class="language-text"><code class="language-text">// First run\ngoatnickels -init-config y\ngoatnickels -serve y</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id="creating-an-account"><a href="#creating-an-account" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>Creating an account</h2>\n<div class="gatsby-highlight">\n      <pre class="language-text"><code class="language-text">// Make an account to store GoatNickels in\ngoatnickels -generate-acct y -save y</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>The <code class="language-text">-save</code> flag will write the account to a keystore file at <code class="language-text">~/.goatnickels/keystore.json</code> and update the account in <code class="language-text">config.json</code>. <strong>Make a backup of the keystore file!</strong> If you lose your key, you will not be able to recover GoatNickels in the account.</p>\n<p>All accounts start with <em>goat_</em> and are followed by a long hash. Raw account balances are in Pellets, the smallest unit of goat money. 1 Pellet = .00000001 GoatNickels.</p>\n<h2 id="mining-goatnickels"><a href="#mining-goatnickels" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>Mining GoatNickels</h2>\n<p>During each consensus voting round (every ten seconds), miners are rewarded GoatNickels based on the amount they have "staked" as a long-term deposit for the right to vote.</p>\n<p><em>Staking to be implemented</em></p>',timeToRead:1,excerpt:"Build the binary Pull  the repo  from Github to the appropriate folder in your 'src' directory under your GOPATH then run the following. Orâ€¦",frontmatter:{title:"GN Quick Start Guide",cover:null,date:null,category:null,tags:null}},tableOfContents:{coolness:"very-cool",chapters:{goat_nickels:{getting_started:[{post:{id:"/Users/smclane/Code/goatsite/content/lessons/gn/quick_start.md absPath of file",childMarkdownRemark:{fields:{slug:"/gn-quick-start-guide"},frontmatter:{title:"GN Quick Start Guide"}}}}],block_data:[{post:{id:"/Users/smclane/Code/goatsite/content/lessons/gn/block_data.md absPath of file",childMarkdownRemark:{fields:{slug:"/block-data"},frontmatter:{title:"Block Data"}}}}],consensus:[{post:{id:"/Users/smclane/Code/goatsite/content/lessons/gn/consensus.md absPath of file",childMarkdownRemark:{fields:{slug:"/consensus"},frontmatter:{title:"Consensus"}}}}]},goat_bucket:{getting_started:[{post:{id:"/Users/smclane/Code/goatsite/content/lessons/gb/quick_start.md absPath of file",childMarkdownRemark:{fields:{slug:"/gb-quick-start-guide"},frontmatter:{title:"GB Quick Start Guide"}}}}]}}}},pathContext:{slug:"/gn-quick-start-guide"}}}});
